    <p class="p" xmlns="">The climate was not better when I was younger.</p>
   </div>
   <div class="list-item" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <p class="p" xmlns="">We can solve environmental problems by returning to the ways of the past.</p>
   </div>
